name: Keep Calm and Cary Grant print, small
description: A cheeky play on the infamous poster from World War II, this print would be a great gift for any fan of the Golden Age of Cinema or screen legend Archibald Alexander Leach. Based on an original design from 2009, this print has been lovingly reproduced into a single-colour design and painstakingly screen printed by Sam and Kay at Get a Grip. Printed on 100% recycled bright white 300gsm stock, the design measures 250 x 350 mm and printed on 320 x 450 mm stock. These will fit in the 420 x 520 mm Ikea RIBBA picture frame. Please note that due to the hand-made nature of this item slight imperfections are to be expected and add to the aesthetic quality of the product. Although not a strictly limited run each design is unique and signed by the artist.
